# ShiftSync Environment Variables

# ==========================================
# 1. OpenAI (Default & Currently Active)
# ==========================================
# Get your key here: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# Note: If this key is provided, the app will use OpenAI (GPT-4o) by default.
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# ==========================================
# 2. Alternative Providers (Requires Code Tweaks)
# ==========================================
# If you want to use Anthropic or Gemini instead, you'll need to modify
# the 'app/api/map/route.ts' file to use their respective SDKs, as the 
# current codebase rigidly expects OpenAI.
#
# Get your key here: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza...
#
# Get your key here: https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant...
